## Upstream Implementation Seeds

This repository contains tracked implementation seed material derived from:

- Project: Paseo
- Repository: https://github.com/getpaseo/paseo
- Upstream commit: 5fc53c576ef0d4dee55455ccc95660703f71b892
- Upstream license: AGPL-3.0
- Upstream copyright: upstream contributors as recorded in that project

The seed material is imported as implementation reference and migration
substrate for New Thoth. It is intentionally allowed to be incomplete,
unwired and temporarily non-compiling until future migration tasks digest it.

The raw upstream cache is local-only and ignored at:

    .agent-os/upstreams/paseo/

It is not part of the tracked source tree and is not project authority.

## Excluded Material

Voice, speech, dictation and audio-specific upstream material is excluded from
the active raw cache and from tracked implementation seeds. New Thoth does not
target voice features in the current MVP line.
